
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI
    participant Frontend
    participant BackendAPI
    participant Receiver
    participant OrderManager
    participant Notifier

    UI->>Frontend: Click place order
    Frontend->>BackendAPI: POST /api/order
    BackendAPI->>Receiver: create order
    Receiver->>OrderManager: create(order)
    OrderManager-->>Receiver: ok
    Receiver->>Notifier: notify(order_placed)
    Notifier->>RestaurantObserver: update()
    Notifier->>DeliveryObserver: update()
    BackendAPI-->>Frontend: return orderId
    Frontend-->>UI: show order id
